enburg |date=5 February 2020 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200206130547/https://www.rbb24.de/politik/beitrag/2020/02/coronavirus-chinesen-botschaft-fremdenfeindlichkeit-berlin.html |archive-date=6 February 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"hbdgB\">{{cite web |url=http://www.leparisien.fr/seine-et-marne-77/coronavirus-de-jeunes-francais-d-origine-asiatique-pris-a-partie-en-seine-et-marne-02-02-2020-8250627.php |title=Coronavirus: de jeunes Fran\u00e7ais d'origine asiatique pris \u00e0 partie en Seine-et-Marne |work=[[Le Parisien]] |date=22 January 2020 |access-date=26 February 2020 |language=fr |last=Cassard |first=Jeanne}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"OI9yc\">{{cite web |url=https://www.franceinter.fr/le-virus-de-la-stigmatisation-anti-chinoise-s-invite-dans-les-cours-d-ecole |title=Coronavirus: en France, la stigmatisation anti-chinoise s'invite dans les cours d'\u00e9cole |work=France Inter |date=1 February 2020 |access-date=26 February 2020 |language=fr |last=Boissais |first=Valentin}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Hco2Q\">{{Cite news |url=https://news.zing.vn/nguoi-a-khong-la-chuyen-bi-ky-thi-virus-corona-con-lam-moi-thu-te-hon-post1041849.html |title=Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1 chuy\u1ec7n b\u1ecb k\u1ef3 th\u1ecb, virus corona c\u00f2n l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n |date=1 February 2020 |work=Zing.vn |access-date=8 February 2020 |language=vi}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"trt33408\">{{Cite news |url=https://www.trtworld.com/turkey/turkish-plane-carrying-wuhan-evacuees-lands-in-ankara-33408 |title=Turkish plane carrying Wuhan evacuees lands in Ankara |date=1 February 2020 |work=[[TRT World]] News |publisher=Turkish Radio and Television Corporation |access-date=3 February 2020 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200203152227/https://www.trtworld.com/turkey/turkish-plane-carrying-wuhan-evacuees-lands-in-ankara-33408 |archive-date=3 February 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NYT-20200326\">{{cite news |last=McNeil, Jr